00:46:22.520 --> 00:46:33.479
In terms of tips for making those run well, like, you have to, like, let there be, like,

00:46:33.479 --> 00:46:34.600
awkward pauses.

00:46:35.399 --> 00:46:42.679
You have to stop and let people's brains, like, catch up so that you give them the opportunity

00:46:42.679 --> 00:46:43.719
